des:
Kalorik Home products help you control home appliance. You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your vacuum.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your vacuum - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your Kalorik Home products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Kalorik Home" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our " Kalorik Home" app;
(3). You need to have some Kalorik Home devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our " Kalorik Home " app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in " Kalorik Home" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Kalorik Home" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Kalorik Home", and you'll be navigated to Kalorik Home login page;
(9). Input your Kalorik Home account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on vacuum.”
“Alexa, turn off  vacuum.”
